THE annual Seekoeirivier Wine Festival is set to take place on the bank of the beautiful Seekoeirivier, situated on the Paradise Beach gravel road, from 10:00 to 18:00 on December 17. Taste and buy great wines from elite wine farms such as Vrede en Lust, Eikendal, Vondeling and Jakkalsvlei. There will be live entertainment, stalls, a food court and entertainment for the kids. Tickets cost R150 per person. For more information, contact Marlize at 082 560 5606 or email orseekoeirivier@hotmail.com.  24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  